<div align="center"><i>by <br>Dr. Prof. Saeedullah Ibrahim</i></div>
            <P><FONT face="Arial, sans-serif" size=2>
<div align="right"><IMG height=21 src="http://www.faizani.com/images/print.gif" width=20><a class=lnkDownLoadBook href="http://www.faizani.com/author/Ppeople_proud.html" target=_blank>Printable Version</a></div>
<p>Dear brothers, Afghanistan has been ruined from every point of view; social, material, economic, as well as seeing a loss in spirituality and its spiritual scholars and personalities. Fortunately, the University of Insight into God (Madrassa -e- Towheed), founded by Mawlana Faizani Sahib which is now under the supervision of Ustad <a class="BodyLinkColor" title="Listen to his live Web Seminars" href="http://www.faizani.com/author/paltalk.html">Mazhabi</a> Sahib has been working for the straight path against all oppressions and cruelty. Ustad <a class="BodyLinkColor" title="Listen to his live Web Seminars" href="http://www.faizani.com/author/paltalk.html">Mazhabi</a> mission should be an example for all of us. If one has been a prisoner, he will clearly know what imprisonment is all about; it is not only the prisoner that suffers tremendously, but those who know him, such as family and friends all end up suffering.  

<p>Mawlana Faizani's struggle for the truth, his writings and research is a great lesson for all of us. Today, we remember Mawlana Faizani, who spent and devoted his entire life for the well being of his people. History remembers the cruel oppressors with abhorrence, however those who sincerely struggled for the truth without ulterior motives are/will be remembered with love, appreciation and become the symbols of light and guidance for the rest of us.  Mawlana Faizani is one such personality of whom the people are truly proud!  He left for us not only great books and enlightening literatures, but also he left us his son, Ustad <a class="BodyLinkColor" title="Listen to his live Web Seminars" href="http://www.faizani.com/author/paltalk.html">Mazhabi</a>; under his leadership the continuation of Mawlana Faizani works and teachings are spreading all over the world. I hope that all scholars and intellectuals unite and follow the foot steps of Mawlana Faizani in their pursuit of peace and unity of our people. For hope, remembrance, and blessing to the spirit of Mawlana Faizani. 

            
